{"tid":628261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[HK No IT]中銀櫃員機本月22日又停服務","createTime":"2018-04-13T16:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T07:27:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0c8c72f6e0489643a2db62c518d6cbee88a8ce","tid":628261,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"全港中銀櫃員機又要熄機！中國銀行(香港)繼本月初因系統提升，要暫停包括櫃員機在內的所有自助服務後，今日(13日)再貼出通告，指因要進行常規的系統維護工作，本月22日凌晨3時30分至凌晨5時30分，該行的自助櫃員機、存鈔機、存支票機等會暫停服務，又指該行已將有關通告上載至官方網頁供客戶查閱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/bkn-20180413200340688-0413_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180413%2Fbkn-20180413200340688-0413_00822_001.html&d=mszPkrQQoR4xrLvcE5owSr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d597d8f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/bkn-20180413200340688-0413_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5e138a599fd2bc4be51334834f81eb6f868fe48b","tid":628261,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d59858fa1b3a5f9bcf638bdabd5427e13593cb7","tid":628261,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e138a599fd2bc4be51334834f81eb6f868fe48b","tid":628261,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"u have ac?"},{"pid":"3a4f5d09df